sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist<br/>(Python / Notebook)
    participant SDK as CodeFlare SDK<br/>(Client Library)
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KubeRay as KubeRay Operator
    participant AppWCtrl as AppWrapper Controller
    participant RayHead as Ray Head Pod<br/>8265/TCP
    participant Dashboard as Ray Dashboard<br/>443/TCP (Route)

    Note over User,Dashboard: Flow 1: Cluster Creation

    User->>SDK: ClusterConfiguration(name, num_workers,<br/>cpu, memory, gpu, local_queue)
    SDK->>SDK: generate_yaml()<br/>Render base-template.yaml<br/>with resource config
    alt AppWrapper enabled
        SDK->>K8s: POST AppWrapper CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s->>AppWCtrl: Reconcile AppWrapper
        AppWCtrl->>K8s: Create RayCluster CR
    else Bare RayCluster
        SDK->>K8s: POST RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    end
    K8s->>KubeRay: Reconcile RayCluster
    KubeRay->>K8s: Create Head Pod, Worker Pods,<br/>head-svc (6379, 8265, 10001)

    Note over User,Dashboard: Flow 2: Cluster Status Check

    User->>SDK: cluster.status() / cluster.details()
    SDK->>K8s: GET RayCluster CR status<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8s-->>SDK: RayCluster status (Ready/Pending/Failed)
    opt AppWrapper mode
        SDK->>K8s: GET AppWrapper CR status<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8s-->>SDK: AppWrapper status (Suspended/Resuming/Running)
    end
    SDK->>Dashboard: GET /api/version (readiness check)<br/>HTTPS via Route, Auth: Bearer Token
    Dashboard-->>SDK: 200 OK / connection error
    SDK-->>User: ClusterStatus + dashboard URL

    Note over User,Dashboard: Flow 3: Ray Job Submission

    User->>SDK: RayJobClient.submit_job(entrypoint)
    SDK->>Dashboard: POST /api/jobs/<br/>8265/TCP or 443/TCP (Route)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (OpenShift)
    Dashboard->>RayHead: Schedule job on Ray cluster
    RayHead-->>Dashboard: Job status updates
    Dashboard-->>SDK: Job ID + status
    SDK-->>User: Job submission result

    Note over User,Dashboard: Flow 4: TLS Certificate Generation

    User->>SDK: generate_tls_cert(cluster_name, namespace)
    SDK->>K8s: GET Secret {cluster}-ca-secret-cert<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8s-->>SDK: CA cert + key (or 404)
    alt CA secret not found
        SDK->>SDK: Generate RSA-2048 CA key<br/>+ self-signed X.509 cert (SHA256)
        SDK->>K8s: CREATE Secret {cluster}-ca-secret-cert<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    end
    SDK->>SDK: Generate worker cert signed by CA
    SDK->>SDK: Write cert/key to local filesystem
    SDK->>SDK: Set RAY_USE_TLS=1, RAY_TLS_*<br/>environment variables
    SDK-->>User: TLS cert paths + env vars configured
